rows.label: qst650306_msg0001
rows.name: Is everyone unharmed?

rows.label: qst650306_msg0002
rows.name:
We're right as rain, and the
Garlus aren't gonna be causing
any more trouble.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0003
rows.name: Well! That is excellent news!

rows.label: qst650306_msg0004
rows.name:
I'll dispatch a squad to the
Genbu Crown right away.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0005
rows.name:
Yep, you don't want some other rotten
blighters to take up residence.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0006
rows.name:
Prince Zeke, everybody, thank you
so much for your assistance. Thanks to
you, we settled this with no casualties.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0007
rows.name: Please accept a token of our gratitude.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0008
rows.name:
Don't worry about it.
We didn't do it for the reward.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0009
rows.name:
That may be so, but King Serich
asked me to give you this himself.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0010
rows.name: Well, in that case, gimme!

rows.label: qst650306_msg0011
rows.name: Talk about a quick change of heart...

rows.label: qst650306_msg0012
rows.name:
Well, at first I thought it might be that
the Luxurian army had clubbed their
wages together to reward us.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0013
rows.name:
The King is loaded, and besides,
he's Zeke's pop. Let him reward
us if he wants.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0014
rows.name:
Indeed. I promise you we didn't
contribute a single gold! Please
just take it.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0015
rows.name: You got it.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0016
rows.name:
If you ever need help again,
don't hesitate to call on us.
We'll be there on wings of justice.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0017
rows.name: Captain Tryhard...

rows.label: qst650306_msg0018
rows.name: Kamuya never change...

rows.label: qst650306_msg0019
rows.name: Nope.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0101
rows.name:
Whew.
Glad we got that over with safely.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0102
rows.name: Yeah.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0103
rows.name:
You really helped us. Especially against
that big one at the end!

rows.label: qst650306_msg0104
rows.name: I'm a Blade. That's just how we roll.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0105
rows.name: Even so...

rows.label: qst650306_msg0106
rows.name:
I'm gonna train hard until you let me
wield that white sword of yours.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0107
rows.name: Haha.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0108
rows.name:
That's the kind of spirit I look
for in my friends.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0109
rows.name: Hah. Let's get stronger together, eh?

rows.label: qst650306_msg0110
rows.name: You bet, Rex.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0111
rows.name:
Hahah...
...So...

rows.label: qst650306_msg0112
rows.name: Erm...

rows.label: qst650306_msg0113
rows.name:
...You do know I'm never going to let
you use Durandal, right?

rows.label: qst650306_msg0114
rows.name:
Whaaat? Not even once? I won't
damage it or anything, I promise!

rows.label: qst650306_msg0115
rows.name: Not in a billion years.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0116
rows.name: But I wanna try dual-wielding...

rows.label: qst650306_msg0117
rows.name:
Nope, no way. Friend or not, it's
never gonna happen.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0201
rows.name:
Whew.
Glad we got that over with safely.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0202
rows.name: Yeah.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0203
rows.name:
You really helped us. Especially against
that big one at the end!

rows.label: qst650306_msg0204
rows.name: I'm a Blade. That's just how we roll.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0205
rows.name:
Even so...
I'm gonna train hard until you let me
wield that white sword of yours.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0206
rows.name: Haha.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0207
rows.name:
That's the kind of spirit I look
for in my friends.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0208
rows.name: There's Captain Tryhard again.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0209
rows.name: Heh, maybe you have a point.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0210
rows.name: Maybe I'll try to tone it down a bit.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0211
rows.name: I won't hold my breath for that.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0212
rows.name: Have a little faith, Nia!

rows.label: qst650306_msg0213
rows.name: I'll do my best to prove you wrong.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0214
rows.name: Good luck with that!

rows.label: qst650306_msg0301
rows.name:
Whew.
Glad we got that over with safely.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0302
rows.name: Indeed.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0303
rows.name:
You proved invaluable. Especially
versus the final Garlus.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0304
rows.name: I'm a Blade. That's just how we roll.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0305
rows.name: Even so...

rows.label: qst650306_msg0306
rows.name:
I intend to train diligently so that
I may someday earn the right to
wield that white sword of yours.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0307
rows.name: Haha.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0308
rows.name:
That's the kind of spirit I look
for in my friends.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0309
rows.name: Friends? Presumptuous, aren't we?

rows.label: qst650306_msg0310
rows.name: What's the problem?

rows.label: qst650306_msg0311
rows.name:
We are comrades-in-arms.
I do not add to the ranks of my
friends so lightly.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0312
rows.name:
Is that all? Well, we'll be best buds
before long, take it from me.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0313
rows.name: Don't hold your breath...

rows.label: qst650306_msg0401
rows.name:
Whew.
Glad we got that over with safely.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0402
rows.name: Tell me about it.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0403
rows.name:
You really helped us. Especially against
that brute at the end!

rows.label: qst650306_msg0404
rows.name: I'm a Blade. That's just how we roll.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0405
rows.name: So, Kamuya...

rows.label: qst650306_msg0406
rows.name: Hmm?

rows.label: qst650306_msg0407
rows.name:
That Durandal of yours is pretty
broken, eh?

rows.label: qst650306_msg0408
rows.name: Broken?

rows.label: qst650306_msg0409
rows.name:
Yes, you know - unreasonably
powerful. When you pull it out, your
enemies are like "This is jolly unfair!"

rows.label: qst650306_msg0410
rows.name:
Say, what are the chances of you
letting your old pal Zeke have a
swing of it sometime?

rows.label: qst650306_msg0411
rows.name:
I thought you might ask that.
It's really only Blades that have the
strength to wield it...

rows.label: qst650306_msg0412
rows.name: Well, you never know until you try.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0413
rows.name:
Sorry, it's gotta be a no. Even if you
were to become the most powerful
Driver in Alst.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0414
rows.name:
That's OK. I'll just nick it
while you're sleeping.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0415
rows.name: Wha?!

rows.label: qst650306_msg0416
rows.name: I guess I'll be switching rooms, then.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0417
rows.name: Hahaha! I'm joking, mate.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0418
rows.name: No you weren't.

rows.label: qst650306_msg0419
rows.name:
Anyway, keep training and getting
stronger. You never know.
